## 🐛 Bug Reports

### BUG-01 — Cart Cleared After Re-Login

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | BUG-01 |
| **Title** | Cart items disappear after logout and re-login |
| **Severity** | 🔴 High |
| **Priority** | 🔴 High |
| **Status** | Open |
| **Environment** | Chrome 120, Windows 11 |
| **Module** | Shopping Cart / Session Management |
| **Reported by** | QA Engineer |
| **Linked TC** | TC-12 |

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Log in to ShopEasy
2. Add any product to the cart
3. Log out
4. Log in with the same account
5. Open the cart

**Expected Result:** Cart should retain previously added items (server-side persistence)

**Actual Result:** Cart is empty after re-login — items not saved to user session

**Root Cause Hypothesis:** Cart stored in localStorage only; not synced to user account on server

**Attachments:** `screenshot_bug01.png`

---

### BUG-02 — Price Not Updated on Manual Quantity Input

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | BUG-02 |
| **Title** | Total price does not recalculate when quantity is typed manually |
| **Severity** | 🟡 Medium |
| **Priority** | 🟡 Medium |
| **Status** | Open |
| **Environment** | Firefox 121, Windows 11 |
| **Module** | Shopping Cart |
| **Linked TC** | TC-11 |

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Add any product to the cart
2. Open the cart
3. Click directly on the quantity field and type `5`
4. Click outside the field (blur event)

**Expected Result:** Total price = unit price × 5

**Actual Result:** Total price stays unchanged

**Note:** Works correctly when using the `+/-` buttons — bug is specific to direct text input

---

### BUG-03 — Shipping Cost Not Shown in Cart Preview

| Field | Details |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | BUG-03 |
| **Title** | Shipping cost is not added to cart total before checkout |
| **Severity** | 🟡 Medium |
| **Priority** | 🟡 Medium |
| **Status** | Open |
| **Environment** | Chrome 120, Windows 11 |
| **Module** | Cart / Checkout |
| **Linked TC** | TC-20 |

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Add a product below the free-shipping threshold
2. View cart total
3. Proceed to checkout and compare totals

**Expected Result:** Cart preview and checkout total both include shipping fee

**Actual Result:** Shipping fee only appears at checkout — cart shows incorrect lower total

